Halalan
Version 0.1.4
http://sourceforge.net/projects/halalan
Copyright (C) 2006-2007 UP Linux Users' Group


VERSION FEATURES:

This release is the basis of the customized version to be used during the University of the Philippines College of Engineering Student Council election which contains new features, minor interface enhancements and some bug-fixes.  This is intended for developers and testers interested in helping the project.


INSTALLATION:

See INSTALL


PURPOSE:

Halalan is an open source web and mobile voting system specifically designed for the University of the Philippines student elections but can be used in other elections with little or no modifications.


DOCUMENT FORMAT:

The formating of files under docs/ are copied from the documents of PHP Timeclock http://timeclock.sourceforge.net.


